description:
2 ASSIGNED OFF-STREET PARKING SPACES. NEWLY RENOVATED. HIGH END FINISHES WITH BRAND NEW APPLIANCES/FIXTURES. THIS FULL SIZE 3 BED 1 BATH WILL NOT LAST. EACH BEDROOM HAS PLENTY OF CLOSET SPACE. LOCATED IN THE PREMIER "CITY POINT" SIDE OF SOUTH BOSTON. STEPS TO M STREET BEACH, SOUTH BOSTON YACHT CLUB, CASTLE ISLAND AND THE NEWLY RENOVATED "CURLEY CENTER". 
Available Oct 1st

Internet/Electric is paid for by the tenant. First/Last months rent and security deposit of 1k is due at signing of the lease. This condo comes with two assigned off street parking spaces.
